{"tid":1138011,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"贊拿斯：羅渣士不喜歡紅迷","createTime":"2019-05-04T08:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T12:47:06.000Z","uid":238051,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"74a17be248aebe15b3513ef3b37384d2efb25d9c","tid":1138011,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T08:50:37.000Z","msg":"利物浦在聯賽積分榜上被曼城以一分領先。如果於週六擊敗紐卡素，利物浦可以回到榜首位置，這將為周一與李斯特城對賽的曼城帶來壓力。 <br />\n<br />\n紅軍的球迷希望羅渣士的李斯特城能夠至少能於曼城身上取得一分，但贊拿斯堅持認為這位前利物浦領隊對紅軍的支持者沒有感情。 <br />\n<br />\n贊拿斯在英國廣播公司第5電台表示 ： &ldquo; 從我的觀點和我所聽到的情況來看，布蘭登羅渣士對利物浦球迷的感覺並不是正面的。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n含錯撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.insidefutbol.com/2019/05/03/heard-brendan-rodgers-not-got-good-feelings-for-liverpool-fans-former-premier-league-star/418866/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insidefutbol.com%2F2019%2F05%2F03%2Fheard-brendan-rodgers-not-got-good-feelings-for-liverpool-fans-former-premier-league-star%2F418866%2F&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8UBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=82296c8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.insidefutbol.com/2019/05/03/heard-brendan-rodgers-not-got-good-feelings-for-liverpool-fans-former-premier-league-star/418866/</a>"},{"pid":"d3d5301b2e67e386efbe4485a4331b7cefddeb59","tid":1138011,"uid":86413,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T08:54:11.000Z","msg":"好快渣蛇係利既地位又變為零"},{"pid":"d48d308bbb4b99956a0b8955d2fbac9433a08ff0","tid":1138011,"uid":25834,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"d3d5301b2e67e386efbe4485a4331b7cefddeb59","tid":1138011,"uid":86413,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T08:54:11.000Z","msg":"好快渣蛇係利既地位又變為零"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T08:59:55.000Z","msg":"不嬲都冇地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /